From ea3571f48953df2cf77a9c4200a7363236736673 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alon Giladi <alon.giladi@intel.com>
Date: Tue, 6 Jun 2023 10:43:05 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: iwlwifi: Use iwl_pnvm_image in reduce power tables flow
Git-commit: ea3571f48953df2cf77a9c4200a7363236736673
Patch-mainline: v6.5-rc1
References: jsc#PED-6081 jsc#PED-6130

Generalize the parsing, loading, and setting of the power-reduce
tables, in order to support allocation of several DRAM payloads
in the future.

Signed-off-by: Alon Giladi <alon.giladi@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Gregory Greenman <gregory.greenman@intel.com>
